{"tid":156484,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［醫學］腳底生咗粒野","createTime":"2017-03-14T18:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T14:07:18.000Z","uid":16520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20dd88877b51589fc8cff7019e90854ea64a3de4","tid":156484,"uid":16520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/15/021751_64c3d7aae1eeca61fae2d2feb2183f56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F15%2F021751_64c3d7aae1eeca61fae2d2feb2183f56.jpg&h=58ba3a25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n生咗果幾星期，行路果時又唔係好覺有粒野，禁落去先有少少痛，好似好小事，所以唔好意思去醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ab30bf586debc246f60f360830f176e7b24aeb","tid":156484,"uid":9252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:21:33.000Z","msg":"雞眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7858f18f79bba197ef17fd3e2ef113248224117","tid":156484,"uid":91296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:24:32.000Z","msg":"Manning watsons買雞眼貼，但有心理準確可能貼成個月都未好.<br />\n想快手無手尾就去醫院用冷凍法ko粒雞眼佢. 如果筆值唔多可以考慮北上搞，一般大陸任何一間正式醫院都做到."},{"pid":"e038c6713143051b345c3918c52d82fbaad6bc60","tid":156484,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:25:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ecca317956df78b63a77f3d88c842bc4e26ae540","tid":156484,"uid":16520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:29:22.000Z","msg":"唔該哂巴打，咁係咪唔整得穿粒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行路要就住嚟行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80b5b9514895bf4d0d25f38ac152ab8fdb42a48","tid":156484,"uid":16520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔該哂巴打，咁係咪唔可以穿粒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=